short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Notifications for Carnival and Soca Lovers

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you a Carnival and Soca Lover? If so this is definitively the site for you. 

At Bahamas Carnival Insider we cover all events leading up to Bahamas Carnival and let you in on some of the biggest giveaways, you just have to be a daily visitor to participate.

We also inject the latest news on Soca artists, DJ's and Carnival costume designers.
